      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW FABLE (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (26.08) in a Grade 4/5 at Geelong. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. LAKEVIEW SNEAKY (1) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 9 length 4th at Traralgon (33.50). Comes through a solid form race last start. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. DR. BEYOND (2) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten 1.75 lengths, (26.12) at Warragul. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Leading chance. PERIODICAL (4) put a gap on his rivals last start. Right in the mix.",
